{"type":"info-page","slug":"jmm/misc/freeonlineaccess.shtml","journal":"jmm","canonical":"https://www.sgmjournals.org/jmm/misc/freeonlineaccess.shtml","title":"JMM - online access free 12 months after publication","bodyHtml":"<a name=\"top\" id=\"top\"></a>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/\"></a> \n        <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/subscriptions/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n              <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n            </td>\n            <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td valign=\"bottom\">\n        <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" border=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#000000\">\n          <tbody><tr>\n            <td>\n\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <br>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <h2>Online access free 12 months after publication</h2>\n  <hr>\n  <p>We are pleased to announce that, as of 15 April 2005, online access to papers in the Journal of Medical Microbiology will be free 12 months after their publication. This policy currently covers papers published from January 2000 onwards for which PDF files are available.</p>\n  <p>A project to convert the contents of all journal volumes into a digitized format is currently underway: the aim of this project is to 'fill the gaps' and ensure that the entire journal back catalogue is available free of charge.</p>\n  <p>Last updated 26 April 2005</p>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/jmm/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" fa